Ontology.primaryTopic: End User Programming in the Internet of Thing
Ontology.description: EUPont is an ontology to model high level rules for Internet of Things End User Programming (IoT-EUP).

Description.comment: Anything with spatial extent, i.e. size, shape, or position. e.g. people, places, bowling balls, as well as abstract areas like cubes.
